/war-and-law" class="nav-link-spot i-arrow-right-after">Overview of War &amp; Law</a><div class=" nav-split"><ul><li><h5 class="h5">Legal Basis</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/treaties-customary-law/geneva-conventions" title="">Geneva Conventions and Commentaries</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/treaties-customary-law" title="">Treaties and customary law</a></li></ul></li><li><h5 class="h5">Featured Publications</h5><ul><li><a href="https://casebook.icrc.org/" title="">How does law protect in war?</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/international-review" title="">International Review of the Red Cross</a></li><li><a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/law-and-policy/" title="">Humanitarian Law &amp; Policy blog </a></li></ul></li><li><h5 class="h5">Services and Resources</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/icrc-advisory-services-international-humanitarian-law" title="">Legal advisory services</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/what-we-do/building-respect-ihl/education-outreach" title="">Learning and teaching IHL</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/law-and-policy" title="">Law and policy platform</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/content/law-and-policy-events" title="">Law and policy events</a></li></ul></li><li><h5 class="h5">Legal Topics</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl" title="">Current debates on IHL</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/protected-persons" title="">Protected persons</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/weapons" title="">Weapons</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/conduct-hostilities" title="">Conduct of hostilities</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/emblem" title="">Use of emblems</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/international-criminal-jurisdiction" title="">Violations of IHL</a><